statements: SELECT project_name, project_location FROM property_development_projects

SELECT project_id, project_name FROM property_development_projects WHERE zoning_regulation LIKE '%residential%'
SELECT project_name, project_location, project_end_date FROM property_development_projects ORDER BY project_end_date ASC, project_location DESC LIMIT 5

SELECT project_name, project_type, project_budget FROM projects ORDER BY project_budget DESC;
SELECT project_name, project_type FROM projects WHERE project_type = 'Construction';

SELECT zone_type, regulation_details FROM zoning_regulations ORDER BY effective_date;
SELECT project_name, project_type, project_budget FROM projects WHERE project_start_date >= '2022-01-01'

SELECT project_name, project_type, project_budget, project_start_date FROM projects WHERE project_budget BETWEEN 10000 AND 50000 ORDER BY project_start_date ASC
SELECT project_name, project_type, project_budget FROM projects WHERE project_type IN ('Research', 'Development') ORDER BY project_type
SELECT * FROM projects;
SELECT project_name, development_phase FROM projects ORDER BY development_phase DESC;
SELECT project_id, project_name, estimated_cost FROM projects WHERE estimated_cost > 50000;
SELECT * FROM market_forecasting WHERE forecast_date = '2023-09-15';
SELECT project_name, predicted_demand FROM projects JOIN market_forecasting ON projects.project_id = market_forecasting.project_id ORDER BY predicted_demand DESC;
SELECT * FROM projects WHERE development_phase='Planning';
SELECT project_name, estimated_cost FROM projects WHERE estimated_cost > 50000;
SELECT project_name, development_phase FROM projects ORDER BY project_name DESC;
SELECT project_name, allowed_height FROM projects JOIN zoning_regulations ON projects.project_id = zoning_regulations.zoning_id;
SELECT project_name, predicted_demand FROM projects JOIN market_forecasting ON projects.project_id = market_forecasting.project_id WHERE predicted_demand > 1000;
SELECT * FROM project_properties;
SELECT project_name, forecasted_market_value FROM project_properties WHERE zoning_category = 'Residential';
SELECT project_name, zoning_category FROM project_properties ORDER BY project_name DESC;
SELECT project_id, project_name FROM project_properties WHERE forecasted_market_value > 500000 ORDER BY forecasted_market_value ASC;

SELECT p.project_name, z.zone_name, m.forecast_date FROM project_properties p JOIN project_zones pz ON p.project_id = pz.project_id JOIN zoning_regulations z ON pz.zone_id = z.zone_id JOIN market_forecast m ON m.forecast_value > p.forecasted_market_value;
SELECT * FROM project_properties;
SELECT project_name, zoning_category FROM project_properties WHERE forecasted_market_value > 10000 ORDER BY project_name ASC;

SELECT p.project_name, z.zone_name, m.forecast_value FROM project_properties p JOIN project_zones pz ON p.project_id = pz.project_id JOIN zoning_regulations z ON pz.zone_id = z.zone_id JOIN market_forecast m ON m.forecast_id = pz.zone_id WHERE m.forecast_date >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT p.project_name, z.zone_name, m.forecast_value FROM project_properties p JOIN project_zones pz ON p.project_id = pz.project_id JOIN zoning_regulations z ON pz.zone_id = z.zone_id JOIN market_forecast m ON m.forecast_id = pz.zone_id WHERE m.projected_growth_rate > 0.05 ORDER BY m.forecast_value DESC;

SELECT p.project_name, z.zone_name, m.forecast_value FROM project_properties p JOIN project_zones pz ON p.project_id = pz.project_id JOIN zoning_regulations z ON pz.zone_id = z.zone_id JOIN market_forecast m ON m.forecast_id = pz.zone_id WHERE p.project_name LIKE 'A%' AND z.building_height_limit <= 50 ORDER BY p.project_name DESC, m.forecast_value ASC;
